@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title FastAPI Items API - Architecture

actor Client

component "FastAPI Router\n(app/api/routes)" as Router
component "Service Layer\n(app/services)" as Service
component "Pydantic Models\n(app/models)" as Models

Client --> Router : HTTP requests
Router --> Service : call business logic
Router --> Models : validate request/response
Service --> Models : create/read model instances

@enduml
